name: famous guitars
description:
The Graphics on the front and back of this Hanes all Cotton, Black Pre-Shrunk Shirt are Outstanding!  The front chest logo is of the Famous Guitar Imprint, done in brilliant Colors.

The back large graphic shows all 11 Guitars used by the worlds most famous guitar Players, such as:  Stevie Ray Vaughn – BB King – Jimi Hendrix – Kurt Cobain – Bo Diddley – Randy Rhodes – Roger McGuinn – Eddie Van Halen – Jimmie Page and Prince.  Each Guitar  is done in an array of colors, each showing the Artist name under their personal Guitar.

Special pricing for bulk sales.
